const light = {
    title: 'light',
    colors:{
        primary: '#000',
        background: '#fff',
        cardBackground: 'hsl(228, 28%, 20%)',
        cardHover: '#333a56',
        textBlue: 'hsl(228, 34%, 66%)',
        text: '#fff',
        upColor: 'hsl(163, 72%, 41%)',
        downColor: 'hsl(356, 69%, 56%)',
        filter: 'invert(100%)',
}
}
export default light
